'''''Pickaxe''''' was a [[Naboo Moon Mining Union]] [[kassoti]] [[Spice/Legends|spice]] [[Transport/Legends|transport]] that ran between [[Naboo/Legends|Naboo]] and [[Rori/Legends|Rori]], captained by [[Calquad Dominé]]. In [[22 BBY/Legends|22 BBY]], it prevented the ''[[Sluissi Wanderlust]]'' from landing in [[Kwilaan Starport/Legends|Kwilaan Starport]].

